comments: Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with Wade (MIA) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Dragic (MIA) gathers the ball and comes to a legal jump stop.
Brunson (DAL) briefly engages Waiters (MIA) as he slips the pick, but does not prevent him from disengaging from the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dragic (MIA) lifts his pivot foot after he has gathered the ball.
Powell (DAL) establishes his screening position in Johnson's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Wade (MIA) extends his arms into Powell's (DAL) back and dislodges him from his obtained position.
Wade (MIA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Nowitzki (DAL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Wade (MIA) slightly extends his leg into Nowitzki (DAL) during his jump shot attempt, but the contact is marginal.
Dragic (MIA) and Brunson (DAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Powell (DAL) steps into Johnson's (MIA) path as he sets the screen and does not extend his arms.
Adebayo (MIA) does not attempt a shot before the expiration of the 24-second clock.
Powell (DAL) is not in a wide screening position in Jones Jr.'s (MIA) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Johnson (MIA) moves along Doncic's (DAL) path without dislodging him and makes marginal contact with his hand as Doncic begins his shooting motion.
Adebayo (MIA) holds Powell's (DAL) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
Waiters (MIA) initiates contact with Powell's (DAL) neck and upper body as he fights over the screen.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Wade (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position on Broekhoff (DAL) as he deflects the pass.
Broekhoff (DAL) makes marginal contact with Wade's (MIA) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Jones Jr. (MIA) cleanly deflects Doncic's (DAL) pass attempt at the end of his drive.
